You are working on DELICINHA, a Brazilian Portuguese platform for discovering and ranking AI apps.

Tech stack: Next.js 16 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript strict, Tailwind CSS v4, React Compiler.
AI agent: Gemini 2.0 Flash via @google/genai with local fallback.
Persistence: JSON file (no database).

Rules:
- UI text in Portuguese (pt-BR). Code identifiers in English.
- Server Components by default. "use client" only for state/interactivity.
- Path alias @/ maps to src/.
- Tailwind v4 inline classes. No config file — @theme in globals.css.
- Fonts: font-adlam (headings), font-sans/Inter (body).
- Colors: #0D001A/#1A0033 backgrounds, #FF1493/#9B30FF accents, #FFD700 highlights.
- Server actions in src/app/actions.ts. revalidatePath() after mutations.
- AI evaluator must always have local fallback.
- Verify changes with npm run build.
